    • Hello World!

    Hi there!

    Thanks for stopping by and checking the site out! If you know what a jailbreak is, then awesome - jump onboard via Facebook and we'll keep you in the loop. If not - feel free to browse this (still-under-construction) website, which will hopefully give you a better idea of what it's all about. I'd also encourage you to read about the hype Jailbreak fundraisers have been generating in Europe - and why it's high time we brought it to Canada!

    If you want to learn more or get in touch, feel free to drop an email to uwjailbreak@gmail.com. That's all for now!
